metadata.name: Ethlizards - Saint Nicholiz #1/5
metadata.description:
Saint Nicholiz

He comes once a year, from out of the sand,  
and travels the land with a bag in his hand.

You better be good cuz he doesn't take bribes,  
at Christmas he brings all nice degens good vibes.

So leave out some cookies... er crickets and flies,  
Saint Nicholiz might bring you new all time highs ðŸŽ…
